_description: William Dunbar, To the King — six five-line stanzas with refrain

CULLl510.First Lines:
Off benefice sir at every feistQuha monyest hes makis maist
                    requeist…
CULLl510.Last Lines:
…Quha maist hes maist dois þane repentAnd hes maist
                    compte to part amang þame
CULLl510.Note:
6 x 5, aabab, incl. refrain ending ‘amang
                    þame’.

CamMagPep2553.First Lines:
Off Benefice schir at everie feistQuha monyast hes makis maist
                    requeist…
CamMagPep2553.Last Lines:
…Quha maist hes þan sall maist repentWith largest compt
                    to pairt amang þame
